OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy and breezy on
OL,6,FSaturday with a few spots of light
OL,7,Frain in the north. Drier in the south,
OL,8,Fbut still largely cloudy. A few
OL,9,Fbrighter spells likely in the
OL,10,Fsoutheast where it will feel warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying cloudy tonight with
OL,13,Fsome light rain and drizzle continuing
OL,14,Fin northern areas. Drier in the south,
OL,15,Fperhaps with a few clearer spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
