OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAfter a cloudy start, cloud
OL,6,Fwill start to lift and break through
OL,7,Fthe morning. Prolonged sunny spells
OL,8,Fwill develop with some warm sunshine
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon, particularly in
OL,10,Fthe south.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,13,Fdrier start from next week with
OL,14,Fincreasing amounts of sunny spells.
OL,15,FStaying largely dry with warm sunshine
OL,16,Fand lighter winds.
